strings: <voice_0x01000F28><se_def>Prince Charmles: Home at last. It feels like a lifetime since we left on our epic journey.

<voice_0x01000F2A><se_def>Prince Charmles: The flags are up! Oh, the bazaar is on!
It must have started while we were away!
<voice_0x01000F2B><se_def>Prince Charmles: I'm going to do a little shopping before I go back to the castle. DIS-MISSED!
<voice_0x01000F2C><se_def>Prince Charmles: If I go back to the castle now, I won't have any time to enjoy the bazaar... Ah!
<voice_0x01000F2D><se_def>Prince Charmles: I'll go back tomorrow. Tonight we stay at the inn. Don't worry. I'll pay for you paupers.
